data.description: BACK ON MARKET, BUYER UNQUALIFIED. PRICE IMPROVED! SPACIOUS 2 BED/3.5 BATH TOWNHOME IN SOUGHT AFTER ARLINGTON POINTE - EASILY TRANSFORMED INTO A 3 BEDROOM!    Features Include: Open Concept Floor Plan, Grand Two-story Foyer, Home Office with Custom Built-in Desk, Media/Bonus Room, Generous Secondary Bedroom, Formal Dining Room, Formal Living Room, Gleaming Hardwood Flooring, 9' Ceilings, Iron Balusters, Upgraded Trim Package Throughout, Chef's Kitchen with Breakfast Bar, Butler's Pantry, Granite Countertops, Custom Backsplash, Stainless Steel Appliances, Gas Cooktop and Double Ovens. The sun-drenched great room boasts a gas stacked-stone fireplace and has direct access to the outdoor living space. Upstairs, the oversized primary retreat offers a large sitting room that may easily be converted into a third bedroom, dual walk-in closets, vaulted ceilings and a spa-like en suite bath with double vanities, soaking tub and a separate shower. On the terrace level you'll find a media/bonus room, full bath and tons of storage. Relax or entertain on the private rear deck overlooking the equestrian center. New Hot Water Heater, AC Units replaced in 2020. Conveniently located near Shopping, Dining, State Bridge Road, Ocee Park, GA-141, and everything Johns Creek has to offer! Click the Virtual Tour link to experience the 3D Walkthrough today.
